name: Power of Love
comments: This is a cover of a song that was originally introduced as a new song ("Power of Love") in a medley with a classic song ( Love Power ).  Donna Summer's version contains no part of Love Power - and is therefore essentially a 'partial' cover of the original medley, though it would be a full cover of "Power of Love" had that been released first as an individual song.
